    "And of the sons of <span class=\"person\">Benjamin</span>; Sallu the son of Meshullam, the son of Hodaviah, the son of Hasenuah,",
    "And Ibneiah the son of Jeroham, and <span class=\"person\">Elah</span> the son of Uzzi, the son of Michri, and Meshullam the son of Shephathiah, the son of <span class=\"person\">Reuel</span>, the son of Ibnijah;",
