    "Of <span class=\"place\">Dan</span>, Azareel the son of Jeroham. These were the princes of the tribes of <span class=\"place\">Israel</span>.",
    "But <span class=\"person\">David</span> took not the number of them from twenty years old and under: because the LORD had said he would increase <span class=\"place\">Israel</span> like to the stars of the heavens.",
    "Joab the son of Zeruiah began to number, but he finished not, because there fell wrath for it against <span class=\"place\">Israel</span>; neither was the number put in the account of the chronicles of king <span class=\"person\">David</span>.",
    "And over the king's treasures was Azmaveth the son of Adiel: and over the storehouses in the fields, in the cities, and in the villages, and in the castles, was Jehonathan the son of Uzziah:",
